OL,2,MHacking APRS to warm my camper van
OL,4,Mwhilst I’m still in the pub
OL,6,CGeoff Robinson
OL,7,CFri 15:50-16:10
OL,8,CStage C
OL,10,GThis brief talk will describe a
OL,11,Gpersonal remote-control protocol that
OL,12,Gcan be run over APRS and potentially
OL,13,Gother similar location messaging
OL,14,Gprotocols. APRS is an amateur VHF/UHF
OL,15,Gad-hoc, wide area, resilient digital
OL,16,Gmesh network relaying position
OL,17,Ginformation. Amateur APRS networks
OL,18,Goperate using AX25 packet radio at 144
OL,19,G& 432MHz and can have a similar range
OL,20,Gper node to UHF LoRa and Meshtastic
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
